TestMatrix (Licensed Product) is protected by copyright, and is distributed
under the following terms.

TestMatrix is an open source tool, developed by OCI and written in 
unix shell, C, and Python (>= 2.1).  It is designed to generate webpages
for displaying the statistics of ACE and TAO builds.

Since TestMatrix is open source and free of licensing fees, you are free to
use, modify, and distribute the source code, as long as you include this
copyright statement.

Note, however, that you may not do anything to the TestMatrix code, such as
copyrighting it yourself or claiming authorship of the TestMatrix code, that
will prevent TestMatrix from being distributed freely using an open source
development model.

